title: CCK Podcast: Owen Sixteen
description:
The Rocket is due for a win after losing 16 straight Rock Paper, Scissors matches. Lil Dicky called his shot on Mailtime back in 2015. Will Chill With Chels get a job at Barstool? When will HQ open back up? Mets fans finally have a chance to destroy the Wilpons.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
